# @name createDriverEmptyFields
POST {{baseUrl}}/drivers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "",
  "lastName": "",
  "identityCard": "",
  "licenseNumber": ""
}

###
# Expected: 400 Bad Request - Validación fallida

### 11.9 Crear Conductor - Fallido (Tipo de contrato inválido)
